Package: markovChains
Type: Package
Title: Simulation, estimation and modeling with Markov chains
Version: 0.1.0
Author: S. Hill
Maintainer: S. Hill <52792611+shill1729@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Provides functions for simulating Markov chains in both discrete and continuous time as well as
    estimating transition probability or transition rate matrices from observed chains. Other features include computing
    stationary distributions and other statistical properties of a chain.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: stats, Matrix, utils
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
